com.android.build.api.transform

Class SecondaryFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.build.api.transform.SecondaryFile

  • public class SecondaryFile
extends java.lang.Object
    A secondary input file(s) for a Transform. A secondary input is part of the transform inputs and can be decorated to indicate if a change to the input would trigger a non incremental Transform.transform(TransformInvocation). call. The collection should only contain one file.

      • supportsIncrementalBuild

        public boolean supportsIncrementalBuild()
        Returns true if this secondary input changes can be handled by the receiving Transform incrementally. If false, a change to the file returned by getFileCollection(org.gradle.api.Project) will trigger a non incremental build.
        Returns:
        true when the input file changes can be handled incrementally, false otherwise.
